p, k, h, t = [0] * 4

for i in range(0, len(s), 3):
    if s[i] == "P":
        p[int(s[i + 1:i + 3])] += 1
    elif s[i] == "K":
        k[int(s[i + 1:i + 3])] += 1
    elif s[i] == "H":
        h[int(s[i + 1:i + 3])] += 1
    elif s[i] == "T":
        t[int(s[i + 1:i + 3])] += 1

if p[1:] > 1 or k[1:] > 1 or h[1:] > 1 or t[1:] > 1:
    print("GRESKA")
else:
    print(13 - sum(p), 13 - sum(k), 13 - sum(h), 13 - sum(t))
